headline: MAA to Present at the Nareit REITweek: 2025 Investor Conference
summary: Mid-America Apartment Communities, Inc., or MAA (NYSE: MAA), today announced that President and CEO, Brad Hill, as well as other members of MAA's executive management team, will present at the Nareit REITweek: 2025 Investor Conference on Wednesday, June 4, 2025, from 8:45 a.m. ET to 9:15 a.m. ET.

headline: MAA Announces Regular Quarterly Preferred Dividend
summary: Mid-America Apartment Communities, Inc., or MAA (NYSE: MAA), today announced a full quarterly dividend of $1.0625 per outstanding share of its 8.50% Series I Cumulative Redeemable Preferred Stock. The dividend is payable on June 30, 2025, to shareholders of record on June 13, 2025.
